caption: As someone who is following a eating regimen. It was amazing to find “get my meals” in Miami, when I moved from NY for a 3 month stay. Their meals are delicious and varied. You have a choice to substitute and choose which calorie intake you would prefer to utilize. Their biggest strength is their customer service. They answer your questions timeously and delivery service is spot on. They haven’t let me down ONCE. Have been using them for a month now.
Excellent food.
Amazing meals and and amazing customer service
You are the best!

Amazing food and service. These guys are the absolute best.  Always deliver on time and the team is ready to help you with whatever you need, specially Lana. She is very friendly, replies promptly to inquiries, and gives you the best discounts 😜
Love the food love the staff , My husband just joined in for his first time. I am constantly looking forward for my next delivery. Thank you

I visited Miami for a week and needed a meal prep service.  Their food was amazing and on top of that, their customer service was incredible. Will definitely use them again next time I'm in town!

Amazing food, great quality and packaging. Reliable and very accomodating. We were stayed at South Beach for 6 days and had a small fridge. Athleticsfit is the best delivery service I've every utilized. The delivery schedule is flexible, the food is delicious and always fresh, and the customer service is stellar  I've been a client with athleticsfit for more than 3 years and they've never gotten an order completely wrong or missed a scheduled delivery.  I had an issue once with getting less ounces than I ordered. I called customer service and they sent me a free meal of choice on my next order to make up for the mixup!  That blew me away and cemented my loyalty. Customer service is what sets many businesses apart from their competitors and Athleticsfit knocks it out of the park consistently for me.  Oh, and you know how you have to spend a certain amount every week or become a member with other food delivery services? Forget that with AF. You can stop and start as often as you want. Another awesome feature that sets them apart from everyone else.  Do yourself a favor and forget all the other delivery services and join me at Athleticsfit.  You'll be glad you did! 😊
Amazing food! When I first tried their meals realized it's the best healthy and delicious option in all Miami Dade!

I ordered from them when I had a busy season at work. Started with create your own meal plan and then tried the 3 meals a day plan. I really liked the food- was a good switch for me, since I was eating frozen lunches and dinners before. The customer service was good too- all my concerns were addressed. Also if never done it before try "create your own meal plan" first to see how you like it and then jump in other meal plans. Ask for discount codes too, I think they still provide new customers with them. Overall good experience and waiting to order from them when get busier at work.
